  "text": "A further outcome of this trial was recognition of the importance of the clinical environment to nurse practitioner education, a finding that is supported by previous research into undergraduate [CITATION_1] and specialist [CITATION_2] ) nurse education. Inherent in this clinical learning aspect is the role of a committed clinical mentor who can facilitate purposeful learning.",
